Class XmlSchemaDocSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.Context
      • org.apache.juneau.BeanContext
        • org.apache.juneau.BeanTraverseContext
          • org.apache.juneau.serializer.Serializer
            • org.apache.juneau.serializer.WriterSerializer
              • org.apache.juneau.xml.XmlSerializer
                • org.apache.juneau.xmlschema.XmlSchemaSerializer
                  • org.apache.juneau.xmlschema.XmlSchemaDocSerializer

  • public class XmlSchemaDocSerializer
extends XmlSchemaSerializer
    Serializes POJO metadata to HTTP responses as XML.
    Media types
    Handles Accept types: text/xml+schema

    Produces Content-Type types: text/xml

    Description
    Same as XmlSchemaSerializer, except prepends <?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?> to the response to make it a valid XML document.
